name: Every woman is a world to discover

metadata.name: Lively
metadata.description:
She is living in her magical world, she is as wise as a whale ( whale is a symbol of wisdom) and as free as a bird ... she is trying to live a healthy life ( those mushrooms are symbol of living healthy) but on the other hand as fragile as purple bubbles... she talks alot but easy going as well . She flows so smooth just like the jellyfish. 
There are much more to discover about her ...
